CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper July 27, 1946, 18, reads: "Visit Courier Plant - Members of the Royal Society of Brownsville were recent visitors at The Pittsburgh Courier plant. Left to right, front row, are: Mmes B. Thompson, Grace Arnett, Florence Johnson, M. Smith, Louise Couzzins, Mary Alston, Sadie Montgomery, Lillian Henry; back row: Vandee Smith, Blanche Wilson, Lavenia Brown, Mary Stamp and E. English. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Members of Royal Society Club of Brownsville, front row from left: B. Thompson, Grace Arnett, Florence Johnson, M. Smith, Louise Couzzins, Mary Alston, Sadie Montgomery, Lillian Henry; back row: Vandee Smith, Blanche Wilson, Lavenia Brown, Mary Stamp and E. English posed in front of Pittsburgh Courier newspaper offices, Hill District
